{"tid":619244,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個90後，今日呢件事令我覺得香港人真係好蠻不講理","createTime":"2018-04-06T12:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T13:22:13.000Z","uid":139768,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7a367454aa6b6541c045d26bcc6f34c89acf9e82","tid":619244,"uid":139768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T12:46:34.000Z","msg":"就係8點嘅時候我係女人街同家樂坊交界行緊，跟著後面有個阿叔話我阻著左佢，咁我同佢講對吾住囉。跟著佢話我串串共，之後就不停撞我。仲恐嚇我話小心俾人打，我同佢理論話:「旺角咁多人，個個阻到你都打人呀」，我拍佢片，佢就不停拍我隻手。其實我最失望係點解香港仲有啲咁野蠻嘅人。認真我拍左佢片，如果多人想睇我就post 岀黎:-，真心覺得啲冇EQ嘅MK阿叔衰過蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下面有兩位惡人嘅相<br />\n( <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/203848_60864f12c6a2e13b32d8bf8dfcb6cbbc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F203848_60864f12c6a2e13b32d8bf8dfcb6cbbc.png&h=a41417bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/204240_8f79a6f4bb9039974df522d59b929285.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F204240_8f79a6f4bb9039974df522d59b929285.png&h=4c0667ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72619c1e5ad972aaf322cf0347e8d38b18de8e0a","tid":619244,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T12:49:11.000Z","msg":"旺角獅豪哥你都夠膽post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主希望唔會俾人斬死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14989b287d5a0746cd9daf023e5bd87ae826faf3","tid":619244,"uid":59192,"like":3,"dis